---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import { GITHUB_URL } from '../consts';
---

<Layout
	title="About — designedbykoda"
	description="Maker designing custom PCBs, ESP32 hardware, and RF tools."
>
	<div class="about">
		<h1>About</h1>
		<div class="prose">
			<p>
				I'm Koda, and I design and build custom electronics for fun. Everything on this site
				started as a rough idea, got sketched into a schematic, routed into a PCB, and eventually
				came back as a real board I could solder up and break.
			</p>
			<p>
				Most of what I build lives somewhere between RF/wireless tools, ESP32-based hardware, and
				smart home devices — usually with a custom enclosure, proper battery management, and
				firmware written from scratch. I care a lot about getting the details right: clean power
				regulation, enclosures that actually fit, and UI that doesn't feel like an afterthought.
			</p>
			<p>
				There's always something new in progress — check the
				<a href="/projects">projects page</a> for the full list, or the
				<a href={GITHUB_URL} target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub</a> for code and design files.
			</p>
		</div>
	</div>
</Layout>

<style>
	.about {
		max-width: 640px;
	}
	.prose p {
		font-size: 1.05em;
	}
</style>
